## Onda-style delivery

Features ship as numbered ondas with a written plan in `docs/plans/` before any code. Plans live ~30–60 tasks each. Never start an Onda without one.

**Onda done = all of**: zero pending tasks in plan, integration suite green (0 failed), full test suite green, `migrate-smoke` green if migrations changed, pre-commit clean, manual smoke of the user-visible feature, branch merged to main.

Use `scripts/harness/onda_done.py --plan <file>` to close an onda. Use `scripts/harness/validate_plan.py <file>` to validate a plan before starting it.
